<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>مَعْهُودٍ، وَهُوَ <span style="color:#008000">(الرَّجُلُ)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَ <span style="color:#008000">(ثَوْبُ)</span>: مَعْرِفَةٌ فِي قَوْلِكَ: <span style="color:#008000">(ثَوْبُ هَذَا)</span>؛ لأَنَّهَا أُضِيفَتْ إِلَى اسْمٍ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مُبْهَمٍ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهُوَ اسْمُ الإِشَارَةِ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(هَذَا)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَ <span style="color:#008000">(ثَوْبِ)</span>: مَعْرِفَةٌ فِي قَوْلِكَ: <span style="color:#008000">(ثَوْبِي)</span>؛ لأَنَّهَا أُضِيفَتْ إِلَى ضَمِيرٍ، وَهُوَ <span style="color:#008000">(يَاءُ المُتَكَلِّمِ)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَ <span style="color:#008000">(ثَوْبُ)</span>: مَعْرِفَةٌ فِي قَوْلِكَ: <span style="color:#008000">(ثَوْبُكَ)</span>؛ لأَنَّهَا أُضِيفَتْ إِلَى ضَمِيرٍ، وَهُوَ <span style="color:#008000">(كَافُ الخِطَابِ)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>